NK041(di)027:1: // bsangs kyi cho ga bde legs kun 'byung rgyags barngana dang bcas pa bzhugs so //
NK041(di)027:2: o rgyan pad+ma 'byung gnas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK041(di)027:3: rgyags barngana 'di la don lnga ste /
NK041(di)027:4: mdzad pa po mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub brnyes pa'i slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis mdzad /
NK041(di)027:5: gnas gang du mdzad na brag dmar dpal gyi bsam yas su mdzad /
NK041(di)027:6: dgos ched gang la mdzad na /
NK041(di)027:7: sngon byung rgyal po'i thugs dam dgongs pa bzhengs pa dang /
NK041(di)027:8: phyi rabs rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi 'dod don sgrub pa'i don du mdzad /
NK041(di)027:10: lam 'phrang bgrod pa la sogs gang 'dod thams cad 'grub /
NK041(di)027:11: gang dngos don du bstan pa la /
NK041(di)027:12: sngon 'gro dngos gzhi rjes gsum las /
NK041(di)027:14: ri rtse 'am khang thog gam chu 'gram la sogs phyogs gtsang sar /
NK041(di)027:15: dar mdung la sogs pa'i rten btsugs pa'i mdun du /
NK041(di)027:18: snam dkar dri ma med pa'i gdan gyi steng du 'bru'i g.yung drung ris bri /
NK041(di)027:19: tshom bu mang du bkod pa'i mthar /
NK041(di)027:20: yon chab bdug spos sogs mchod pa rnam pa mang po dang /
NK041(di)027:22: chos skyong spyi'i dmar gtor gru gsum /
NK041(di)027:23: rigs drug spyi'i dkar gtor zlum po /
NK041(di)027:25: 'byung po spyi'i bgegs gtor gyi dmar gtor dang lnga /
NK041(di)027:26: sku glud sder cha gang dang drug bsham /
NK041(di)027:47: sder cha gtsang mar dkar gsum dang mngar gsum zas sna 'dzom gang che /
NK041(di)027:48: chang rin po che sna lnga'i phye ma dang bcas pa bsham /
NK041(di)027:49: de'i mdun dbus mar bsangs bshos gtsang mar zas snas bskor ba bsham /
NK041(di)027:50: de'i g.yas su chang phud gral thabs dang /
NK041(di)027:52: rin po che'i phye ma btab pa'i chu sna'i snod bsham /
NK041(di)027:53: kun gyi g.yas rol du shing sna'i me dang /
NK041(di)027:54: phye mar gyis bkang ba'i snod bsham /
NK041(di)027:55: phyogs mtshams su dar po che dang mdung dang mda' dar sna gzug /
NK041(di)027:56: rnga dung cha lang la sogs pa'i rol mos bskor ba'i nang du /
NK041(di)027:57: bsangs bshos la nye bar bsangs g.yog sbreng ba bcas te 'dug la /
NK041(di)027:58: dang po skyabs su 'gro ba ni /
NK041(di)027:59: rang gi mdun gyi nam mkhar bla ma yi dam
NK041(di)027:60: mkha' 'gro sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dang
NK041(di)027:61: bcas pa sprin phung gtibs pa lta bur gsal bar
NK041(di)027:62: gyur / nam mkha'i gnas su nam mkha' gang ba yi //
NK041(di)027:63: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK041(di)027:64: sangs rgyas chos dang 'phags pa'i dge 'dun la //
NK041(di)027:65: bdag dang 'gro drug gus pas skyabs su mchi //
NK041(di)027:68: thun mong dang mchog gnyis las /
NK041(di)027:70: ji ltar sngon gyi bde gshegs kyis //
NK041(di)027:71: sems can kun la phan don du //
NK041(di)027:72: byang chub thugs ni bskyed pa ltar //
NK041(di)027:73: de bzhin 'gro la phan don du //
NK041(di)027:74: byang chub sems ni bskyed bgyi zhing //
NK041(di)027:75: ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar bgyi //
NK041(di)027:76: ma grol ba rnams grol bar bgyi //
NK041(di)027:77: dbugs ma phyungs rnams dbugs dbyung zhing //
NK041(di)027:81: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK041(di)027:82: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK041(di)027:83: yin par shes pa'i bdag nyid du //
NK041(di)027:84: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK041(di)027:86: gsang sngags bla na med pa'i sdom pa bzung ba ni /
NK041(di)027:87: ji ltar sngon gyi rgyal ba sras bcas dang //
NK041(di)027:88: rig 'dzin mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK041(di)027:89: phyi nang gsang ba mchog gi dam tshig dang //
NK041(di)027:90: sdom pa brgya mtsho mtha' yas gzung ba ltar //
NK041(di)027:91: deng nas bdag kyang lam chen der zhugs te //
NK041(di)027:92: 'gro la phan phyir ma lus gzung bar bgyi //
NK041(di)027:94: de nas mchod pa byiin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK041(di)027:97: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+hahsarba d+har+m+aahswa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK041(di)027:98: mchod rdzas kyi nyes skyon rnams mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK041(di)027:99: stong pa'i ngang las las rin po che'i snod yangs
NK041(di)027:100: shing rgya che ba rnams kyi nang du +aahh+aum 'od
NK041(di)027:101: du zhu ba las byung ba'i mchod yon /
NK041(di)027:108: rol mo la sogs pa dwangs shing thogs pa med
NK041(di)027:109: pa zag pa med pa'i bde ba khyad par can
NK041(di)027:110: skyed pa nam mkha' dang mnyam par gyur /
NK041(di)027:113: badz+ra push+pe badz+ra d+h+au pe badz+ra +aa lo badz+ra gan+d+he badz+ra ni wid+ya badz+ra shap+da +aahmh'u /
NK041(di)027:114: de nas sman raka gtor gsum byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK041(di)027:115: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aah b+han+d+ha gzhal yas khang nang du //
NK041(di)027:116: bcud ni rigs lnga yab yum ste //
NK041(di)027:117: sbyor mtshams byang sems bdud rtsir zhu //
NK041(di)027:118: 'ching grol med pa'i rang bzhin gyur //
NK041(di)027:119: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u h+r+aihth+aah nyon mongs chags pa rnam dag pa //
NK041(di)027:120: rak+ta bde ba'i ngo bor gyur //
NK041(di)027:121: ma h+aa ba lim ta te dzo ba lim ta
NK041(di)027:122: ba la ba te gu h+ya sa ma ya h'u
NK041(di)027:123: h+r+aihth+aah gtor ma 'dod yon lnga ldan gyi //
NK041(di)027:124: phun tshogs nam mkha' gang bar 'gyur //
NK041(di)027:125: de nas bdag bskyed gsal gdab pa ni /
NK041(di)027:127: stong pa'i ngang las pa las pad+ma dang +aahls zla
NK041(di)027:128: ba ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du
NK041(di)027:129: / rang gi rig pa yi ge h+r+aihdakara po ring
NK041(di)027:130: cha tsheg drag dang bcas pa las 'od zer 'phros
NK041(di)027:132: sems can gyi don byas tshur 'dus yongs su gyur
NK041(di)027:133: pa las rang nyid skad cig gis rig 'dzin chen
NK041(di)027:134: po pad+ma 'byung gnas ats+aar+ya gzhon nu'i tshul can sku
NK041(di)027:135: mdog dkar la dmar ba'i mdangs dang ldan pa /
NK041(di)027:136: zhabs rgyal po rol ba'i 'dug stangs kyis bzhugs pa /
NK041(di)027:137: sngags pa'i chas rdzogs mthing nag dar gyi phod kha /
NK041(di)027:138: rab byung chas rdzogs le brgan dar gyi chos gos gser gyi ha ris can /
NK041(di)027:139: 'khor los sgyur rgyal chas rdzogs za 'og ber smug gsol ba /
NK041(di)027:140: rig pa'i dbang lnga rdzogs shing ye shes lnga dang
NK041(di)027:141: ldan pa'i brdar phyag g.yas gser gyi rdo rje rtse
NK041(di)027:143: gsang ba'i dbang rdzogs pa'i brdar phyag g.yon mtshan ldan
NK041(di)027:144: thod pa bdud rtsis gang ba lte bar bsnams pa
NK041(di)027:145: / yum sbas pa'i tshul du dug gsum rtsad gcod kyi kha t+wam ga /
NK041(di)027:146: gsum pa'i dbang rdzogs pa'i brda mtshon pa'i me long
NK041(di)027:147: dril bu dar dpyangs g.yer khas brgyan pa gru mo
NK041(di)027:149: sku lnga'i dbang rdzogs rigs lnga'i rtags kyis spras pa'i 'dab ldan pad+ma'i snyan zhu dbu la gsol ba /
NK041(di)027:150: sku dang ye shes mtshon pa'i me long nyi zla
NK041(di)027:151: dar sna lnga dang theg mchog a ti'i lta ba
NK041(di)027:152: mtshon pa'i rgod ldem gyis spras pa /
NK041(di)027:153: 'ja' tshon 'od lnga'i gur khang dang rig 'dzin dpa'
NK041(di)027:154: bo mkha' 'gro sprin gyi phung po lta bu'i dbus
NK041(di)027:155: na mtshan dpe yongs rdzogs snang stong sgyu ma'i tshul
NK041(di)027:158: de las 'od zer 'phros pas zangs mdog dpal gyi
NK041(di)027:159: ri bo pad+ma 'od kyi gzhal yas nas o rgyan
NK041(di)027:160: gyi gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas la 'khor rgyal ba
NK041(di)027:161: rab 'byams kyis bskor ba badz+ra sa m+aa dzah de
NK041(di)027:163: h+r+aih sngon gyi bskal pa'i dang po la //
NK041(di)027:164: o rgyan yul gyi nub byang mtshams //
NK041(di)027:165: pad+ma ge sar sdong po la //
NK041(di)027:166: ya mtshan mchog gi dngos grub brnyes //
NK041(di)027:169: khyed kyi rjes su bdag sgrub kyi //
NK041(di)027:170: byin gyis brlab phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK041(di)027:171: gnas mchog 'di ru byin phob la //
NK041(di)027:172: sgrub mchog bdag la dbang bzhi skur //
NK041(di)027:173: bgegs dang log 'dren bar chad sol //
NK041(di)027:174: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK041(di)027:175: +aahmh'u badz+ra gu ru pad+ma thod phreng rtsal badz+ra sa
NK041(di)027:176: ma ya dza sid+d+hi pha la h'u +aah badz+ra sa
NK041(di)027:178: a ti p+au hoh pra t+ai dza hoh zhes pas bzhugs su gsol /
NK041(di)027:180: rgyas par las gzhung ltar dang /
NK041(di)027:182: badz+ra gu ru pad+ma sa pa ri w+aa ra badz+ra push+pe +aahmh'u /
NK041(di)027:183: d+h+au pe +aa lo ke gan+d+he nee wi d+y+aa shap+da
NK041(di)027:184: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta rak+ta ba lim ta
NK041(di)027:185: kh+aa hi / zhes lan bdun nam gsum gyis phul la /
NK041(di)027:187: snyan pa'i dbyangs dang bcas pas 'di skad do //
NK041(di)027:189: bstan pa 'di la ngo mtshar rmad du byung //
NK041(di)027:190: 'jig rten mgon gyur pad+ma rgyal po ni //
NK041(di)027:191: rigs ni za hor rgyal po'i rigs su 'khrungs //
NK041(di)027:192: o rgyan yul du sgro 'dogs ma lus bcad //
NK041(di)027:193: bsil ba tshal du dngos grub ma lus brnyes /
NK041(di)027:194: kha ba can du bstan pa rgyas par mdzad //
NK041(di)027:195: lho nub rnga yab gling phran yul du byon //
NK041(di)027:196: zhe sdang gdong dmar srin po'i kha gnon mdzad //
NK041(di)027:197: mya ngan mi 'da' 'gro ba'i gnyen gcig pu //
NK041(di)027:198: sku gsung che mchog badz+ra he ru ka /
NK041(di)027:199: dus gsum mnyam nyid bla ma dus 'dir dran //
NK041(di)027:200: bdag dang dbyer med bla ma he ru ka /
NK041(di)027:201: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor dag pa chen po 'dir //
NK041(di)027:202: mi 'gyur lhun grub pad+ma rgyal po dang //
NK041(di)027:203: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gros byin gyis rlobs //
NK041(di)027:204: +aahmh'u badz+ra gu ru pad+ma sid+d+hi h'u /
NK041(di)027:205: de nas mdun bskyed gsal gdab pa ni /
NK041(di)027:207: stong pa'i ngang las mdun du pa las pad+ma /
NK041(di)027:208: a las zla ba'i gdan yangs shing rgya che ba /
NK041(di)027:209: stong gsum 'jig rten gyi khams dang mnyam pa'i steng
NK041(di)027:210: du h+r+aihls spyan ras gzigs +aa ro lika rgyan cha
NK041(di)027:211: lugs kha sar+pa ni lta bu /
NK041(di)027:212: sku che ba rnam snang gangs chen mtsho dang mnyam pa /
NK041(di)027:213: zhing khams thams cad skus khyab cing sku la zhing khams thams cad snang ba /
NK041(di)027:214: ba spu'i bu ga thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab par gyur /
NK041(di)027:215: de'i gtsug tor nas mgrin pa yan chad la dkon mchog sri zhu'i mgron /
NK041(di)027:216: thugs ka nas lte ba'i bar la mgon po yon tan gyi mgron /
NK041(di)027:217: sku smad kyi cha la rigs drug snying rje'i mgron /
NK041(di)027:218: pad gdan gyi cha la tshe rabs lan chags kyi mgron rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK041(di)027:219: ye shes pa rnams spyan drangs nas gnyis med du bzhugs par bsams la 'di skad do //
NK041(di)027:221: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten khams bzhugs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:222: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro dang //
NK041(di)027:223: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK041(di)027:224: 'phags pa nyan thos rang rgyal dang //
NK041(di)027:226: sems can rnams kyi skyob pa dang //
NK041(di)027:227: bdag gi bsam pa rdzogs slad du //
NK041(di)027:228: gnas 'dir mchod phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK041(di)027:229: tshangs pa dang ni brgya byin dang //
NK041(di)027:230: rgyal chen bzhi dang phyogs skyong bcu //
NK041(di)027:231: phyi nang lha srin sde brgyad rnams //
NK041(di)027:232: mchod sbyin don du spyan 'dren na //
NK041(di)027:233: bstan pa bsrung phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK041(di)027:234: srid pa'i rtse mo man chad nas //
NK041(di)027:235: mnar med dmyal ba yan chod du //
NK041(di)027:236: khams gsum rigs drug sems can rnams //
NK041(di)027:237: byams thugs brtse bas mgron la gshegs //
NK041(di)027:238: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu sogs //
NK041(di)027:239: tshe rabs grangs 'das lan chags bgegs //
NK041(di)027:240: mchod mgron don du spyan 'dren na //
NK041(di)027:241: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' la nyon //
NK041(di)027:242: zhi ba'i yid kyis 'khod par gyis //
NK041(di)027:243: dzahmh'u ba hoh zhes spyan drangs la /
NK041(di)027:244: dz+ny+aa na lo ka sa pa ri wa ra pad+ma s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra ka ma l+aa ya s+t+wam /
NK041(di)027:247: mdun bskyed 'phags pa'i tshogs las gzugs sgra dri ro
NK041(di)027:248: reg bya chos la sogs pa mchod pa'i lha mo
NK041(di)027:250: nam mkha' gang ba'i mchod pa'i sprin gyis 'phags pa'i
NK041(di)027:251: tshogs rnams mnyes shing dam can rnams thugs dam bskang
NK041(di)027:252: ba dang / rigs drug rnams 'dod pas tshims nas
NK041(di)027:253: sha 'khon byang ste mgron rnams dgyes pa'i 'dod dgu'i
NK041(di)027:254: 'byor pas dang bar snang thams cad gang bar gyur
NK041(di)027:255: ba dang / par dmigs la / mchod pa'i tshig ni /
NK041(di)027:256: mchod yon me tog bdug pa dang //
NK041(di)027:257: snang gsal dri mchog zhal zas dang //
NK041(di)027:258: rol mo la sogs mchod pa'i sprin //
NK041(di)027:259: ji snyed nam mkha'i khams gang 'bul //
NK041(di)027:260: dz+ny+aa na lo ka sa pa ri wa ra ar+g+ham
NK041(di)027:261: p+aa d+yam push+pe d+h+au pe +aa lo ke gan+d+he nee
NK041(di)027:262: wi d+y+aa shap+da p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra
NK041(di)027:263: s+pha ra na sa ma ye +aahmh'u /
NK041(di)027:264: de nas gtor ma 'bul ba ni /
NK041(di)027:265: mgron rigs rnams kyi ljags rdo rje'i sbu gu can gyis gtor ma drangs shing gsol bar gyur /
NK041(di)027:266: gu ru d+he wa d+aa ki n+ai d+harma p+aa la
NK041(di)027:267: dz+ny+aa na lo ka p+aa la sa pa ri w+aa
NK041(di)027:268: ra i dam ba lim ta kha kha kh+aa hi
NK041(di)027:269: kh+aa hi / lan gsum gyis phul la /
NK041(di)027:270: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma 'dod pa'i yon tan bsam
NK041(di)027:271: gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa 'di nyid 'bul
NK041(di)027:272: zhing bsngo ba'i gnas su gyur pa ni /
NK041(di)027:273: dkon mchog sri zhu'i mgron du gyur pa rje btsun
NK041(di)027:274: rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal ldan bla
NK041(di)027:276: yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs sangs rgyas byang
NK041(di)027:277: chub sems dpa'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams la 'bul
NK041(di)027:278: lo // bdag sogs sems can thams cad kyi tshogs
NK041(di)027:279: gnyis rdzogs shing sgrib gnyis byang nas myur du mngon
NK041(di)027:280: par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar byin gyis brlab tu
NK041(di)027:281: lo // gsol / mgon po yon tan gyi mgron
NK041(di)027:282: du gyur pa dpal ye shes kyi mgon po lcam
NK041(di)027:283: lo // gsol / dral / dpal mgon bdun cu
NK041(di)027:284: rtsa lnga sogs gtsug lag khang gi srung ma dang
NK041(di)027:285: lo // gsol / dral / / bstan pa la
NK041(di)027:286: dad pa'i dam can mthu stobs can 'khor dang bcas
NK041(di)027:288: mnyes shing tshims nas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang /
NK041(di)027:289: sems can thams cad bde zhing skyid pa'i phrin las rgya chen po mdzad du gsol /
NK041(di)027:290: rigs drug snying rje'i mgron du gyur pa 'gro ba
NK041(di)027:291: rigs drug lam rgyud lnga skye gnas bzhis bsdus pa'i
NK041(di)027:292: sems can rnams la sbyin no //
NK041(di)027:293: rang rang gi spyod yul du mos pa dang mthun
NK041(di)027:294: pa'i chos dang zang zing gi 'byor pa dpag tu
NK041(di)027:295: med pas tshims te so so'i sdug bsngal las grol
NK041(di)027:296: nas myur du sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par
NK041(di)027:297: gyur cig / lan chags kyi mgron du gyur pa
NK041(di)027:298: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu sogs lan chags dang
NK041(di)027:299: bu lon sha 'khon gnyer ba'i 'byung po rnams la
NK041(di)027:300: gyur cig / sbyin no // 'dod pa'i longs spyod phun sum tshogs pas tshims nas /
NK041(di)027:301: gnod pa dang gdug pa'i bsam pa thams cad zhi
NK041(di)027:302: zhing phan pa byang chub kyi sems dang ldan par
NK041(di)027:303: gyur cig / ces mgron rnam bzhi la bsngosa nas /
NK041(di)027:304: bye brag tu gzhi bdag gtor ma ni /
NK041(di)027:305: a k+aa ro sogs lan gsum gyi mthar /
NK041(di)027:306: stong gsum spyi phud 'dzam gling dang /
NK041(di)027:307: khyad par bod yul kha ba can na gnas pa'i gter bdag chen po rnams dang /
NK041(di)027:308: yul lha gzhi bdag gnyug mar gnas pa rnams la 'bul lo //
NK041(di)027:309: 'gal rkyen sel zhing mthum rkyen sgrub pa dang /
NK041(di)027:310: gnas mgron gyi dam tshig srungs la 'go zhing sdong grogs gnyan po mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)027:312: mgron rigs rnams dgyes pas rang gis ji ltar bcol ba'i phrin las thogs med du sgrub par bsam /
NK041(di)027:313: de nas bsangs dngos la 'jug pa ni /
NK041(di)027:314: dri zhim po'i ba lu mkhan dkar spos kyi bsangs
NK041(di)027:315: kyi me la dkar gsum mngar gsum zas sna 'bru
NK041(di)027:316: sna sman sna rin po che dar sna spos sogs
NK041(di)027:317: bsreg / ja chang zho 'o ma sogs btung ba sna tshogs kyis mchod nas /
NK041(di)027:318: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da l+ai ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK041(di)027:320: bsang rdzas mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK041(di)027:321: stong pa'i ngang las las byung ba'i rin po che
NK041(di)027:322: las grub pa'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang
NK041(di)027:323: du +aahmh'u 'od du zhu ba las byung ba'i lha
NK041(di)027:324: rdzas dri bzang gi mchod pa /
NK041(di)027:325: rtsi shing sna tshogs kyi dud pa /
NK041(di)027:326: zhal zas phye mar gyi 'o skol gsur gyi dud sprin chen po /
NK041(di)027:327: du ba ye shes kyi bdud rtsis sa dang bar snang thams cad gang ba /
NK041(di)027:336: ri rgyal las dpangs mtho ba /
NK041(di)027:337: rgya mtsho las gting zab pa /
NK041(di)027:338: zhing rdul las grangs mang ba /
NK041(di)027:340: rgya che nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa /
NK041(di)027:342: 'chi ba bslu ba'i bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur /
NK041(di)027:345: du ba'i lha mo sku mdog sngon mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK041(di)027:346: g.yas bdud rtsi'i bum pa 'dzin zhing g.yon sman gyis gang ba'i gzhong ba 'dzin pa /
NK041(di)027:347: zhal 'dzum bag gi mdangs dang ldan pa /
NK041(di)027:348: g.yas bdud rtsi'i bum pa nas bdud rtsi'i rgyun dpag
NK041(di)027:349: tu med pa thu lu lu byung bas 'go ba'i
NK041(di)027:350: lha la sogs pa la khrus byas /
NK041(di)027:351: ro bag la sogs grib dang mi gtsang ba thams cad chus bkrus nas dag par byas /
NK041(di)027:352: g.yon sman gyis gang ba'i gzhong pa nas sman dpag
NK041(di)027:353: tu med pa thu lu lu byung bas klu gnyan
NK041(di)027:354: sa bdag rmugs pa thams cad sangs nas sangs rgyas
NK041(di)027:355: kyi bka' rjes su dran te bdag cag ci 'dod
NK041(di)027:356: pa'i sdong grogs byed par gyur /
NK041(di)027:357: rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas dbyangs snyan pos mgrin gcig tu 'di skad do //
NK041(di)027:358: e ma ho de dgongs su gsol //
NK041(di)027:359: gling bzhi'i mchog gyur lho yi 'dzam bu'i gling //
NK041(di)027:360: 'dzam gling byang shar ri rgyal rta rna 'dzin //
NK041(di)027:361: de la 'chi med bdud rtsi'i shing gsum skyes //
NK041(di)027:362: rtsa ba mkhan pa gser gyi me tog can //
NK041(di)027:363: sked par shing skyes g.yu shug ral pa 'dzin //
NK041(di)027:364: rtse mo ba lu dung gi me tog can //
NK041(di)027:365: yon tan ldan pa'i shing mchog de la ni //
NK041(di)027:366: 'chi ba med pa'i dngos grub bdud rtsi'i gnas //
NK041(di)027:367: nam zla dus bzhir sngo zhing dri ngad ldan //
NK041(di)027:368: 'di ltar shing mchog yon tan khyad par can //
NK041(di)027:369: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyi byin rlabs kyis //
NK041(di)027:370: sems can 'khrul pa'i rnam rtog bsal slad du //
NK041(di)027:371: lha 'dre mi gsum srid 'byung rten 'brel gyis //
NK041(di)027:372: las dang bsod nams smon lam rgyu mthun pa //
NK041(di)027:373: 'chi ba med pa'i yon tan bdud rtsi'i shing //
NK041(di)027:374: dri zhim spos dang dung spriin nam mkhar 'khrigs //
NK041(di)027:375: lha 'dre mi gsum rmugs shing 'thibs pa sel //
NK041(di)027:376: 'od gsal me lce 'od zer phreng ba 'phro //
NK041(di)027:377: ma rig rmongs pa'i mun nag thams cad sel //
NK041(di)027:378: me stag tsh+wa zhing sreg pa'i ngar ldan pas //
NK041(di)027:379: mnol chags mi gtsang ljan ljin sreg par byed //
NK041(di)027:380: de ltar yon tan khyad 'phags shing gsum 'di //
NK041(di)027:381: chos dbyings rnam par dag pa'i byin rlabs dang //
NK041(di)027:382: skyabs gnas dkon mchog gsum gyi bden tshig dang //
NK041(di)027:383: drang srong rig 'dzin rnams kyi grub pa'i mthus //
NK041(di)027:384: lha 'dre mi gsum srid pa'i dpe lugs kyis //
NK041(di)027:385: bsam sbyor dag pas gcig tu bka' bgros nas //
NK041(di)027:386: lha 'dre mi gsum 'khrugs na bsang ba'i thabs //
NK041(di)027:387: rme mnol gtsang btsog byung na bsang ba'i thabs //
NK041(di)027:388: dngos grub bar chad 'dres na bsang ba'i thabs //
NK041(di)027:389: bden rdzun legs nyes 'dres pa bzang ngan 'bring gsum
NK041(di)027:390: 'dres pa cho ga nor 'khrul byung na lha 'dre
NK041(di)027:391: mi gsum byad grib bsang rmi ltas mtshan ma ngan
NK041(di)027:392: pa la nye mo rtsis ngan pa dbang po sgo
NK041(di)027:393: lnga 'gag pa mgon lha g.yang lha mnol na 'khon
NK041(di)027:394: 'dzin phrag dog byung na cho 'phrul rnam rtog byung
NK041(di)027:395: na yul mkhar brtsigs nyes byung na srung ma thugs
NK041(di)027:396: dam g.yel na sa bdag klu gnyan 'khrugs na lo
NK041(di)027:397: zla zhag dus ngan na nyi zla gza' skar ngan
NK041(di)027:398: na bsangs khrus cho ga zab mo grub pa'i mthus
NK041(di)027:399: // legs par spyad pas mi shes mi mthong med //
NK041(di)027:400: drang srong bden pa'i tshig gis mi 'grub med //
NK041(di)027:401: rten 'brel cho gas mi tshangs gang yang med //
NK041(di)027:402: rgyu rkyen tshogs pas thams cad 'grub par 'gyur //
NK041(di)027:403: lag len byas pas thams cad dag par gsungs //
NK041(di)027:404: e ma ho de dgongs su gsol //
NK041(di)027:405: de ring bdag cag yon mchod 'khor bcas kyi //
NK041(di)027:406: mi gtsang nyams grib mkhon 'dzin phrag dog dang //
NK041(di)027:407: dal yams bar chod zhi zhing bsang ba'i phyir //
NK041(di)027:408: mkhyen cing gzigs pa'i lha rnams dgongs su gsol //
NK041(di)027:409: de ring gnam la gza' dang skar ma bzang //
NK041(di)027:410: sa gzhi dpyad legs yon tan 'dod dgu tshang //
NK041(di)027:411: bar du dus tshod tshes grangs bkra shis so //
NK041(di)027:412: bsangs dang zhi ba'i cho ga byed pa la //
NK041(di)027:413: nyi ma dge zhing rgyu skar bzang po yi //
NK041(di)027:414: sangs rgyas byams che dgra bcom zag pa zad //
NK041(di)027:415: sangs rgyas rkang gnyis gtso ste bden pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)027:416: chos nyid chags pa med de bden pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)027:417: dge 'dun mi phyed 'dun pa bden pa'i mchog /
NK041(di)027:418: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK041(di)027:419: bsangs kyi cho ga legs par grub par shog /
NK041(di)027:420: e ma ho de dgongs su gsol //
NK041(di)027:421: bsangs rdzas mchod do kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin //
NK041(di)027:422: tsan dan dkar po a shug pha yis bsangs //
NK041(di)027:423: tsan dan dmar po a shug ma yis bsangs //
NK041(di)027:424: sman gyi rgyal po a ka ru yis dri yi
NK041(di)027:425: rgyal po du ru ka yis ba lu dkar po
NK041(di)027:426: lha yi spos kyis shug pa lo bzang g.yu 'od
NK041(di)027:427: 'bar bas mkhan pa dkar po rtsi bzang dri yis
NK041(di)027:428: phur mong dkar po glang chen ngad kyis bla med
NK041(di)027:429: skyabs mchog bla ma bka' brgyud rkang gnyis gtso gyur
NK041(di)027:430: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bag chags sbyong mdzad dam chos
NK041(di)027:431: dkon mchog bsod nams zhing gyur 'phags pa'i dge 'dun
NK041(di)027:432: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor yi dam lha tshogs zhing rnams
NK041(di)027:433: skyong mdzad dpa' bo mkha' 'gro bstan pa skyong mdzad
NK041(di)027:434: chos skyong srung ma phyi rgyud rdo rje rigs kyi
NK041(di)027:435: srung ma bka' srung rgyud srung gter gyi srung ma
NK041(di)027:436: slob dpon pha mes brgyud kyi srung ma dben gnas
NK041(di)027:437: chos 'khor yongs kyi srung ma bsnyen sgrub skal ldan
NK041(di)027:438: yongs kyi srung ma mthu dpung sdong grogs byed pa'i
NK041(di)027:439: srung ma bdag cag dpon slob yon mchod 'khor bcas
NK041(di)027:440: kyi // nyin gyi bya ra byed pa'i lha bsangs so //
NK041(di)027:441: mtshan gyi mel tshe byed pa'i lha bsangs so //
NK041(di)027:442: kha 'dzin shags 'debs byed pa'i lha bsangs so //
NK041(di)027:443: chu la zam pa brag la them skas dang //
NK041(di)027:444: mun par sgron me byed pa'i lha dgra la so byed gnyen la bya gtong dang //
NK041(di)027:445: dug la sman gtong nad la rtsi gsol dang //
NK041(di)027:446: bdud kyi dpung bcom 'dre yi gnya' gnon pa //
NK041(di)027:447: dmag dpung g.yul ngo zlog pa'i lha bsangs so //
NK041(di)027:448: mdun nas bsu zhing rgyab nas skyel ba dang //
NK041(di)027:449: bar na don grub yul du bu nor skyong //
NK041(di)027:450: byes su mi rta'i rdzi bo byed pa dang //
NK041(di)027:451: phan tshun yul 'khor skyong ba'i lha rgyab brten mthu dpung lus srung byed pa dang //
NK041(di)027:452: gtan gyi pho lha yul gyi dgra lha dang //
NK041(di)027:453: pha mes mtshun lha ma phyi'i sman lha dang //
NK041(di)027:454: zas nor g.yang lha rno mtshon ngar lha dang //
NK041(di)027:455: yul rigs sa bdag khams rigs klu gnyan dang //
NK041(di)027:456: 'byung ba nam zla dus bzhi'i sa bdag dang //
NK041(di)027:457: spar kha sme ba lo dang zla ba'i lha //
NK041(di)027:458: gza' skar zhag grangs dus tshod tshes grangs lha //
NK041(di)027:459: phyi nang lha srin sde brgyad mthu chen bsangs //
NK041(di)027:460: khams gsum mnga' dag srid gsum dbang sgyur ba //
NK041(di)027:461: stong gsum dregs pa mthu chen ma lus dang //
NK041(di)027:462: ri rab gling bzhi gser gyi ri bdun dang //
NK041(di)027:463: rol pa'i mtsho bdun lcags ri mu khyud dang //
NK041(di)027:464: rgya mtsho chu klung nam mkha' nyi zla'i khyim //
NK041(di)027:465: dur khrod nags tshal ri bo'i khrod gnas pa'i //
NK041(di)027:466: lha dang klu dang mi'am ci la sogs //
NK041(di)027:467: dri za grul bum mkha' lding lto 'phye dang //
NK041(di)027:468: gnod sbyin 'byung po 'phrog ma'i tshogs bcas bsangs //
NK041(di)027:469: ri rgyal khong seng rgya mtsho'i gling bar dang //
NK041(di)027:470: rin chen ri bo nor bu'i gling gnas pa'i //
NK041(di)027:471: lha klu drang srong mngon shes smon lam dbang //
NK041(di)027:472: sna tshogs gzugs sprul rdzu 'phrul can rnams bsangs //
NK041(di)027:473: sa 'og gter dang grub pa'i bcud dang ni //
NK041(di)027:474: rtsi sman ljon shing lo tog bsrung ba'i lha //
NK041(di)027:475: gter bdag gnod sbyin ma mo mi'am ci //
NK041(di)027:476: dri za srin po'i tshogs bcas thams cad bsangs //
NK041(di)027:477: du bas steng phyogs sa bla'i srid pa bsangs //
NK041(di)027:478: me lces sa steng bar snang lha 'dre me stag
NK041(di)027:479: sa 'og klu gnyan srid pa dri ngad phyogs bcu'i
NK041(di)027:481: nang bcud skye 'gro sems can thams cad dus gsum
NK041(di)027:482: pha ma 'gro ba rigs drug tshe rabs snga phyi'i
NK041(di)027:484: khyad par bod yul kha ba can gnas pa'i //
NK041(di)027:485: bod kyi mgur lha chen po bcu gsum dang //
NK041(di)027:486: mtha' yi dge bsnyen chen po nyi shu gcig /
NK041(di)027:487: bod khams skyong ba'i brtan ma bcu gnyis dang //
NK041(di)027:488: yul gyi gzhi bdag mkhar gyi rtse lha dang //
NK041(di)027:489: sgo lha stag g.yag khyim lha gel thung dang //
NK041(di)027:490: thab lha yu mo zhing lha tshangs pa dang //
NK041(di)027:491: lam lha don grub rta lha dmag dpon dang //
NK041(di)027:492: phyugs lha rma g.yang nor lha'i rgyal po dang //
NK041(di)027:493: tshong lha don 'grub dgra lha'i rgyal po dang //
NK041(di)027:494: mchod par 'os pa'i mgron rigs tshogs rnams la //
NK041(di)027:495: phye mar spos dang dri bsung ngad dang ldan //
NK041(di)027:496: zhal zas 'dod rgu sna tshogs phud kyis mchod //
NK041(di)027:497: tshe srings dpal skyed rigs brgyud bzang po spel //
NK041(di)027:498: kha rje dbang thang snyan grags chen po skyed //
NK041(di)027:499: bdag cag yon mchod mi nor 'khor bcas kyi //
NK041(di)027:500: rnam rtog gzung 'dzin la nye ngan pa rnams //
NK041(di)027:501: mi mtho mgon skyabs lha la mthol te bsangs //
NK041(di)027:502: nya mtho gnas pa'i chu la mthol te sha mtho
NK041(di)027:503: gnas pa'i ri la lha 'dre mi gsum nyi zla
NK041(di)027:504: gza' skar dang // sa 'og klu dang sa steng btsan rnams dang //
NK041(di)027:505: sa bla steng gi gza' skar mthol te mkhyen gzigs
NK041(di)027:506: ye shes lha la mthol te de ltar mthol zhing
NK041(di)027:508: nyon mongs bag chags nyes skyon dag byas nas //
NK041(di)027:509: mi gtsang nyams grib byur yug ngan pa kun //
NK041(di)027:510: bsangs khrus cho ga'i bden pas thur du bsal //
NK041(di)027:511: lus ngag yid gsum mnol ba'i nyes skyon ni //
NK041(di)027:512: rmug pa ri mgo rmugs pas gtums 'dra dang //
NK041(di)027:513: mnol chags shing 'go dbyi mong non 'dra dang //
NK041(di)027:514: nyams grib nyi zla gza' yis bzung 'dra rnams //
NK041(di)027:515: bsangs khrus rten 'brel cho gas thur du bsal //
NK041(di)027:516: dme mnol sdig sgrib thab gzhob 'khon gsum gyis //
NK041(di)027:517: 'khon 'dzin phrag dog nyes pa'i skyon la sogs //
NK041(di)027:518: mgon skyabs lha srung thugs dang 'gal ba rnams //
NK041(di)027:519: bsangs khrus cho ga zab mo grub pa'i mthus //
NK041(di)027:520: mnol chags rmongs pa'i nyams grib dag pa dang //
NK041(di)027:521: rkyen ngan bar gcod nad gdon zhi ba dang //
NK041(di)027:522: phas rgol rbod gtong gnod pa zlog par mdzod //
NK041(di)027:523: 'dod dgu'i bsam pa yid bzhin sgrub pa dang //
NK041(di)027:524: tshe ring nad med longs spyod 'phel ba dang //
NK041(di)027:525: sa skyong yul khams bde legs bkra shis te //
NK041(di)027:526: bla med byang chub thob pa'i rgyur gyur cig /
NK041(di)027:527: bsangs kyi cho ga dge legs kun 'byung zhes bya ba rdzogs so //
NK041(di)027:528: de nas rgyags barngana gyi cho ga dngos la 'jug pa ni /
NK041(di)027:529: mgron rigs rnams re re bzhin barngana pa'i mtshams su
NK041(di)027:530: bsangs phud drangs pa'i ras ma dang zas sna tshogs
NK041(di)027:531: mchod 'bru dang bcas pa blugs la bshams te /
NK041(di)027:532: phud 'thor ba dang chu sna dang chang phud sbreng zhing /
NK041(di)027:533: shing sna'i bsangs de khar phye mar 'bru sna me tog sna tshogs dang /
NK041(di)027:534: rin po che'i phye ma me la bsreg cing rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas 'di skad do //
NK041(di)027:536: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro dang //
NK041(di)027:537: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK041(di)027:538: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod lha //
NK041(di)027:539: phyi nang srung ma'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK041(di)027:540: gsang sngags rig sngags lha rnams dang //
NK041(di)027:541: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
NK041(di)027:542: phyi nang srung ma dam tshig can //
NK041(di)027:544: 'jig rten gnas kyi mchog gyur pa'i //
NK041(di)027:545: sgrub gnas byin chen thams cad dang //
NK041(di)027:546: gzhan yang sa 'og sa steng gi //
NK041(di)027:547: gnas bdag chen po thams cad dang //
NK041(di)027:548: 'khor du gtogs pa'i sde brgyad kyis //
NK041(di)027:549: stong gsum khyab pa'i mthu rtsal can //
NK041(di)027:550: che dgu gnyan dgu thams cad dang //
NK041(di)027:551: gtsug lag khang dang dben gnas kyi //
NK041(di)027:552: srung ma gnyan po thams cad dang //
NK041(di)027:553: gzhan yang lha klu gnod sbyin dang //
NK041(di)027:554: dri za grul bum mkha' 'gro sogs //
NK041(di)027:555: barngana par 'os pa'i mgron rnams dang //
NK041(di)027:556: sa bdag klu gnyan thams cad kun //
NK041(di)027:557: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba dang //
NK041(di)027:558: sgrub pa'i sdong grogs bya ba dang //
NK041(di)027:559: dgon gnas bar chad bsal ba dang //
NK041(di)027:560: dgra dang bgegs rnams gzhom pa dang //
NK041(di)027:561: nad gdon gnod pa la sogs dang //
NK041(di)027:562: chags che nyam nga bzlog pa dang //
NK041(di)027:563: 'dod pa thams cad bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK041(di)027:565: 'dir gshegs bshams pa'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK041(di)027:566: bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par mdzod //
NK041(di)027:567: bdag dang rgyu sbyor yon bdag gi //
NK041(di)027:568: yid la re ba skong ba dang //
NK041(di)027:569: kun kyang bshad pa'i chos la nyon //
NK041(di)027:570: byin rlabs dngos grub dkyil 'khor nas //
NK041(di)027:571: sku lnga ye shes lnga ldan mchog /
NK041(di)027:572: sgrub brgyud bla ma'i tshogs rnams la //
NK041(di)027:574: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK041(di)027:575: chos sku kun bzang la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:576: chos sku'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:578: mtshan dper 'bar ba'i zhing khams nas //
NK041(di)027:579: zhi khro rab 'byams la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:580: longs sku'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:581: phyag 'tshal sna tshogs gdul bya'i zhing khams nas //
NK041(di)027:583: sprul sku'i bla ma thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:584: phyag 'tshal 'og min chos kyi pho brang nas //
NK041(di)027:585: drug pa rdo rje 'chang chen dang //
NK041(di)027:586: rtsa brgyud bla ma'i tshogs rnams la //
NK041(di)027:587: phyag 'tshal khyad par 'gro ba'i gnyen gcig pu //
NK041(di)027:588: o rgyan pad+ma'i rgyal po la //
NK041(di)027:589: phyag 'tshal sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis rlobs //
NK041(di)027:590: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK041(di)027:591: sprul sku'i lha tshogs thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:592: phyag 'tshal bcom ldan rgyal ba rigs lnga la //
NK041(di)027:593: phyag 'tshal yum lnga rin chen phreng ba la //
NK041(di)027:594: phyag 'tshal phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:595: phyag 'tshal dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:596: phyag 'tshal zhi khro dpal chen 'khor bcas la //
NK041(di)027:597: phyag 'tshal rigs gsum mgon po 'khor bcas la //
NK041(di)027:598: phyag 'tshal gdung ba sel ba la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:599: 'phags par rang rgyal thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:600: phyag 'tshal 'od srung chen po la sogs pa //
NK041(di)027:601: nyan thos chen po thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:602: phyag 'tshal b+ha ra d+h+wa dza la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:603: gnas brtan chen po bcu drug la //
NK041(di)027:604: phyag 'tshal nam mkha'i snying po la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:605: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:606: phyag 'tshal tshogs gnyis rgya mtsho rdzogs par mdzod //
NK041(di)027:607: in+d+ra bo d+hi la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:608: grub chen brgyad po thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:609: phyag 'tshal sa ra ha pa la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:610: grub chen brgyad cu rtsa bzhi la //
NK041(di)027:611: phyag 'tshal klu sgrub snying po la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:612: rgyan drug mchog brgyad thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:613: phyag 'tshal don yod zhags pa la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:614: kri ya bya rgyud lha rnams dang //
NK041(di)027:615: pad+ma brtsegs pa la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:616: u pa spyod rgyud lha rnams la //
NK041(di)027:617: phyag 'tshal ngan song sbyong ba la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:618: yo ga rnal 'byor lha rnams dang //
NK041(di)027:619: gsang 'dus rdo rje gdan bzhi dang //
NK041(di)027:621: rdo rje phur pa la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:622: ma h+aa a nu bla med kyi //
NK041(di)027:623: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:624: phyag 'tshal mi nub byang chub sems kyi lung //
NK041(di)027:625: kun bzang rdo rje sems dpa'i tshogs //
NK041(di)027:626: snying po don gyi lha rnams la //
NK041(di)027:627: phyag 'tshal 'jam dpal sku dang pad+ma gsung //
NK041(di)027:628: phur pa phrin las la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:629: sgrub pa bka' brgyad lha rnams la //
NK041(di)027:630: phyag 'tshal nub phyogs o rgyan la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:631: dur khrod chen po thams cad kyi //
NK041(di)027:632: ma sring mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho la //
NK041(di)027:633: phyag 'tshal gnas dang nye ba'i gnas dang phul //
NK041(di)027:634: nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i mkha' 'gro dang //
NK041(di)027:635: srung ma zhing skyong thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:637: 'dod rgu'i re ba skang du gsol //
NK041(di)027:639: mchod yon me tog bdug spos dri //
NK041(di)027:640: zhal zas rol mo gtor ma dang //
NK041(di)027:641: sku glud bsangs phud sna tshogs kyis //
NK041(di)027:643: srung ma gnyan po thams cad dang //
NK041(di)027:644: lha klu gnod sbyin dri za sogs //
NK041(di)027:645: che dgu gnyan dgu thams cad barngana //
NK041(di)027:646: na bza' lhab lhub sna tshogs dang //
NK041(di)027:647: rin chen lnga yi phreng ba yis //
NK041(di)027:648: lha yi dbang po tshangs pa dang //
NK041(di)027:649: brgya byin gser gyi phye mas barngana //
NK041(di)027:650: rgyal chen sde bzhi stag gis barngana //
NK041(di)027:651: shel sgong nag po spyi dkar dang //
NK041(di)027:652: sha khrag dmar gyi gtor ma yis //
NK041(di)027:653: ma h+aa k+aa la lcam dral dang //
NK041(di)027:654: legs ldan nag po 'khor bcas barngana //
NK041(di)027:655: rgyan cha'i mchod pa sna tshogs dang //
NK041(di)027:656: bdud rtsi sha khrag gser skyems kyis //
NK041(di)027:657: dpal ldan lha mo 'khor bcas phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod gtor dang //
NK041(di)027:658: bya nag khyi spyang dom dred dang //
NK041(di)027:659: bsangs phud spyan gzigs sna tshogs kyis //
NK041(di)027:660: sngags bdag shan pa gza' mchog dang //
NK041(di)027:661: dmar nag dam can la sogs pa //
NK041(di)027:662: dam can rgya mtsho 'khor bcas lha rnams 'dod yon sna lngas barngana //
NK041(di)027:663: ma mo me tog phreng bas klu rnams dkar gsum
NK041(di)027:664: gtor mas gnyan rnams mngar gsum dar zab sa bdag
NK041(di)027:665: gser dngul rin chen lha mo brtan ma bum pas
NK041(di)027:666: dri za dri dang gsur gyis gshin rje sha chang
NK041(di)027:667: gtor mas lto 'phye grul bum mii'am ci //
NK041(di)027:668: mkha' lding mchod dang gtor mas gnod sbyin rlung lha drang srong rnams //
NK041(di)027:669: gser g.yu rba dang smyug mas dge bsnyen sha dang chang gis lha 'dre yid kyi gzugs can rnams //
NK041(di)027:670: yid dang mthun pa'i gtor mas btsan rnams ja dang
NK041(di)027:671: dar dkar klu bdud sbrul dang sbal bas lan chags
NK041(di)027:672: mgron rnams gtor mas dam sri gnod byed 'byung po
NK041(di)027:673: rnams // sku glud dar zab gtor mas rgya mtsho nang gi klu chen brgyad //
NK041(di)027:674: chu rta rgyan dang bcas pas bar snang gnas pa'i gza' chen brgyad //
NK041(di)027:675: nas nag ra nag snying gis rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang //
NK041(di)027:676: blon po sum cu rtsa bdun rnams //
NK041(di)027:677: rin chen gser dngul phye mas 'phrog ma ma bu lnga brgya'i tshogs //
NK041(di)027:678: changs bu dag gi gtor mas rigs kyi srung ma thams cad la //
NK041(di)027:679: so sor dgyes pa'i gtor mas sgo bzhi'i srung ma 'khor bcas rnams //
NK041(di)027:680: rin chen dar zab dong tses lha srung gnyan po khyed rnams kyis //
NK041(di)027:681: bdag cag yon mchod 'khor bcas kyi //
NK041(di)027:682: bsam pa sgrubs la re ba skongs //
NK041(di)027:683: 'khor srungs rkyen zlog bar chod sol //
NK041(di)027:684: bkra shis bde legs phun tshogs mdzod //
NK041(di)027:686: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK041(di)027:687: byang chub thugs su chud pa'i gnas //
NK041(di)027:688: rdo rje gdan gyi sa bdag barngana //
NK041(di)027:689: rgya gar lho nub ri chen po //
NK041(di)027:691: ri bo ta la'i sa bdag rdo rje gdan gyi byang phyogs nas //
NK041(di)027:692: bya rgod phung po'i ri dang ni //
NK041(di)027:693: spos ngad ldan pa'i ri bo yi //
NK041(di)027:694: sa bdag gnyan po thams cad barngana //
NK041(di)027:695: ts+aa ri ts+aa gong la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:696: rgya gar shar phyogs yul rnams kyi //
NK041(di)027:697: sa bdag gnyan po thams cad bsil ba tshal gyi dur khrod dang //
NK041(di)027:698: rngam pa sgra sgrogs tshang tshing 'khrigs //
NK041(di)027:699: ha ha rgod pa la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:700: dur khrod brgyad kyi sa bdag rgyal po'i khab dang yangs pa can //
NK041(di)027:701: mnyan yod gnas bcas la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:702: grong khyer yul 'khor thams cad kyi //
NK041(di)027:703: sa bdag gnyan po thams cad gzhan yang kha che o rgyan yul //
NK041(di)027:704: li yul bal yul la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:705: sa bdag gnyan po 'jig rten gsum na man+d+ha ra //
NK041(di)027:707: sa bdag ma dros la sogs mtsho rnams dang //
NK041(di)027:709: chu chen rnams kyi sa bdag ti se gangs ri la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:710: mgul lha gnyan po thams cad ma pham klu gnyan la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:711: sa bdag gnyan ri bo gan+d+ho la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:712: li yi sa bdag thams cad lcang ra smug po la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:713: sogs yul gzhi bdag gnyan rnams gzhan yang gru gu zhang zhung dang //
NK041(di)027:714: gar log la sogs mtha' 'khob yul //
NK041(di)027:715: gzhi bdag gnyan po thams cad rgya gar rgya nag hor dang 'jang //
NK041(di)027:716: bal yul bod yul la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:717: gzhi bdag gnyan po khyad par mnga' ris dbus gtsang dang //
NK041(di)027:718: mdo khams gzhi bdag gnyan po barngana //
NK041(di)027:719: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK041(di)027:720: 'khor srung rkyen zlog bar chad sol //
NK041(di)027:721: bsam pa sgrubs la re ba skongs //
NK041(di)027:722: bkra shis bde legs phun tshogs mdzod //
NK041(di)027:724: yul ni rdo rje'i brag dmar gyi //
NK041(di)027:725: sring gcig gangs dkar sha med ma //
NK041(di)027:726: chibs su dre'u rta rkang gsum chibs //
NK041(di)027:727: bshos bu snying dang gtor mas barngana //
NK041(di)027:728: yul ni rma chen spom ra yi //
NK041(di)027:729: sring gcig kha rag khyung btsun ma //
NK041(di)027:730: chibs su gyi ling kha dkar chibs //
NK041(di)027:731: bshos bu snying yul ni dbu ru'i nyin tshal gyi //
NK041(di)027:732: sring gcig rdo rje g.yu sgron ma //
NK041(di)027:733: chibs su chu rta sngon po chibs //
NK041(di)027:734: bshos bu yul ni man+d+ha de ba yi //
NK041(di)027:735: sring gcig rdo rje kun grags ma //
NK041(di)027:736: chibs su chu glang sngon po chibs //
NK041(di)027:737: bshos bu yul ni lho yul de nyid kyi //
NK041(di)027:738: sring gcig skyi mthing g.ya' ma skyong //
NK041(di)027:739: chibs su gser sha yu mo chibs //
NK041(di)027:740: bshos bu yul ni dpe med lte ba yi //
NK041(di)027:741: sring gcig khug chos g.ya' ma bsil //
NK041(di)027:742: chibs su rus sbal mgo dgu chibs //
NK041(di)027:743: bshos bu snying yul ni bal yul gser phug na //
NK041(di)027:744: e ka dz+aa ti ral gcig ma //
NK041(di)027:745: chibs su g.yu 'brug sngon po chibs //
NK041(di)027:746: bshos bu yul ni na len+d+ha ra na //
NK041(di)027:747: btsan la rol pa'i sman gcig ma //
NK041(di)027:748: chibs su dre'u rta rkang gsum bshos bu yul ni kong yul kong phug na //
NK041(di)027:749: sring gcig gangs kyi g.yu bun ma //
NK041(di)027:750: chibs su stag mo ri khra bshos bu yul ni mang yul mang rting na //
NK041(di)027:752: chibs su 'brong bu dar ma bshos bu yul ni dbu ru snying po yi //
NK041(di)027:753: byang gi ma ting ting mo btsun //
NK041(di)027:755: bshos bu yul ni sbugs yul rgan tshal gyi //
NK041(di)027:756: d+ha lha btsan mo gdug pa 'dul //
NK041(di)027:757: chibs su dom nag snying dkar chibs //
NK041(di)027:758: bshos bu brtan ma chen mo khyed rnams kyis //
NK041(di)027:759: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK041(di)027:760: bsam pa sgrubs la re ba skongs //
NK041(di)027:761: bkra shis bde legs phun tshogs mdzod //
NK041(di)027:763: bod yul kun gyi gzhi bdag ni //
NK041(di)027:764: che dgu gnyan dgu thams cad barngana //
NK041(di)027:765: rdo rje legs pa la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:766: gtsang gi g.yas ru nyin sribs kyi //
NK041(di)027:767: gzhi bdag gnyan po thams cad kha rag khyung btsun la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:768: gtsang gi g.yon ru nyin sribs kyi //
NK041(di)027:769: gzhi bdag gnyan po thang lha bar lha la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:770: dbu ru nyin sribs gzhi bdag sham po gangs bzang la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:771: g.yon ru nyin sribs gzhi bdag yar 'brog g.yu mtsho
NK041(di)027:772: phyug mo byang gi gnam mtsho phyug mo stod kyi
NK041(di)027:773: lha rgod mdung rtse 'od de gung rgyal la sogs
NK041(di)027:774: pa'i // nyang po 'ol kha'i gzhi bdag sgam po dpal ri la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:775: dwags po'i gzhi bdag gnyan po kong btsun de mo la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:776: kong po'i yul gyi gzhi bdag rdo rje grags skyes la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:777: mon yul rdo dang klo rnams kyi //
NK041(di)027:778: gzhi bdag gnyan po sku lha mkha' ri la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:779: lho brag yul gyi gzhi bdag nag sogs chu rgyud dge bsnyen dang //
NK041(di)027:780: a la rngod kyi gzhi bdag rdu yi nyin sribs gzhi bdag lho yi rong lha rgyal mtshan dang //
NK041(di)027:781: rong btsan kha ba dkar po dang //
NK041(di)027:782: dbang chen lha mo mched brgyad dang //
NK041(di)027:783: dmag dpon dgra 'dul dbang phyug dang //
NK041(di)027:784: smug ri mo nam la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:785: tsha ba sgang gi gzhi bdag kim gyi thod rgol smag zhu dang //
NK041(di)027:786: gze yi smag g.yor gwa pa dang //
NK041(di)027:787: lce yi brag la mda' zug dang //
NK041(di)027:788: zla snying dkar nag sum mdo dang //
NK041(di)027:789: rtsi yi bang rgod mthon po dang //
NK041(di)027:790: rgya ma rdo ti gangs dkar mched brgyad dang //
NK041(di)027:791: zla yi gzhi bdag thams cad klu ni mi mgon dkar po sogs //
NK041(di)027:792: smar khams yul gyi gzhi bdag lha yi dge bsnyen dkar po ste //
NK041(di)027:793: 'gyogs byed sdong ra la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:794: 'bri chu nyin sribs gzhi bdag ldan gyi wang snye smre gyu dang //
NK041(di)027:795: ger mtsho ri dmar dbang zhu dang //
NK041(di)027:796: mtshams lha'i gzhi bdag gnyan rnams 'dzab dang shab ze la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:797: spo 'bor sgang gi gzhi bdag shar gyi rma chen spom ra ni //
NK041(di)027:798: rma rigs sum brgya drug cu mched //
NK041(di)027:799: sring lcam bzhi bcu zhe lngar bcas //
NK041(di)027:800: rma lung nyin sribs gzhi bdag be'u yi ni dug mtsho dang //
NK041(di)027:801: stong ra yi ni nag mtsho dang //
NK041(di)027:802: de 'um chad mtsho dkar mo dang //
NK041(di)027:803: khri shog rgyal mo'i mtsho dang ni //
NK041(di)027:804: btsong kha yi ni mtsho sngon dang //
NK041(di)027:805: mtsho sman rgyal mo mched lnga dang //
NK041(di)027:806: skye ri gnyan po la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:807: btsong kha nyin sribs gzhi bdag e che ri dang ha la shan //
NK041(di)027:808: dga' dang byang ngos gzhi bdag rma lung dan tig ri bo'i lha //
NK041(di)027:809: gzhong dkar tig ka la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:810: mdo khams sgang gi gzhi bdag gzhong shod la bo che la sogs //
NK041(di)027:811: dbyar mo thang gi gzhi bdag rtsi yi 'dus ri
NK041(di)027:812: mthon po spo ri brag dmar sgang rgyud spo ri'i
NK041(di)027:813: shel lung phyug mo grol gyi g.ya' lung ral gsum
NK041(di)027:814: rmang grol ral gsum gzhi bdag dgu rim bzhi gsum
NK041(di)027:815: gzhi bdag snye gong snyen dmar gzhi bdag snyan gong
NK041(di)027:816: nyin sribs gzhi bdag brag dmar bya rgod la sogs
NK041(di)027:817: pa'i // sta chu'i gzhi bdag klu gnyan lha srin sdig pa ma bye ba'i //
NK041(di)027:818: 'o de ral gsum gzhi bdag shin tu khro gtum che ba yi //
NK041(di)027:819: rgyal mo rong gi gzhi bdag 'jang ri smug po la sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:820: 'jang yul gzhi bdag thams cad shar phyogs rgya nag 'o de shan //
NK041(di)027:821: ri bo rtse lnga sogs pa'i //
NK041(di)027:822: rgya nag yul gyi gzhi bdag lha klu gnod sbyin dri za dang //
NK041(di)027:823: che dgu gnyan dgu thams cad barngana //
NK041(di)027:824: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK041(di)027:825: re ba thams cad skong ba dang //
NK041(di)027:826: bkra shis bde legs phun tshogs mdzod //
NK041(di)027:828: gzhan yang stong gsum 'dzam gling yul //
NK041(di)027:829: sa 'og sa steng sa bla yi //
NK041(di)027:830: gzhi bdag gnyan po thams cad barngana //
NK041(di)027:831: sa la gnas pa'i sa bdag chu la gnas pa'i
NK041(di)027:832: chu bdag brag la gnas pa'i brag btsan yul la
NK041(di)027:833: gnas pa'i gzhi bdag 'phrang la gnas pa'i gzhi bdag
NK041(di)027:834: la la gnas pa'i gzhi gru zam gnas pa'i gzhi
NK041(di)027:835: gzhi byes 'go ba'i gzhi bdag gzhi bdag chen po
NK041(di)027:836: khyed rnams kyang // mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul so sor che //
NK041(di)027:837: dpal dang 'byor pa so sor mnga' ris mnga' thang
NK041(di)027:838: mdzad pa'i phrin las mchod pa'i 'os su so sor
NK041(di)027:839: che // de bas gzhi bdag gnyan rnams la //
NK041(di)027:842: sngon gyi thugs dam brtser dgongs te //
NK041(di)027:843: dgyes pa'i mchod yon bzhes nas kyang //
NK041(di)027:844: bdag gi re ba bskang du gsol //
NK041(di)027:845: barngana 'os khyed rnams barngana pa yis //
NK041(di)027:846: bkra shis bde legs phun tshogs mdzod //
NK041(di)027:848: gzhan yang barngana par 'os pa'i mgron //
NK041(di)027:849: ming dang mtshan nas ma thon pa'i //
NK041(di)027:850: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro dang //
NK041(di)027:851: srung ma zhing skyong thams cad barngana //
NK041(di)027:852: lha dang drang srong thams cad yul lha nor lha nang lha dang //
NK041(di)027:853: lam lha gnyan po thams cad gzhan yang dus gsum pha ma dang //
NK041(di)027:854: khams gsum rigs drug thams cad yi dwags rnams dang bgegs rnams dang //
NK041(di)027:855: lan chags snying rje'i mgron rnams barngana //
NK041(di)027:856: glo bur lhag pa'i mgron rnams dang //
NK041(di)027:857: lhag ma'i mgron rigs thams cad barngana //
NK041(di)027:858: pham rgyal med par thob nas kyang //
NK041(di)027:859: yid la re ba rdzogs par mdzod //
NK041(di)027:861: de ltar mgron rigs thams cad kyi //
NK041(di)027:862: mnga' ris spyan lam so so ru //
NK041(di)027:863: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'dis barngana pas //
NK041(di)027:864: longs spyod nam mkha'i mdzod gyur te //
NK041(di)027:865: gang la ci 'dod thob par shog /
NK041(di)027:866: rgyags barngana chen mo 'di mdzad pas //
NK041(di)027:867: mgron rigs barngana pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK041(di)027:868: bdag gi don rnams 'grub par shog /
NK041(di)027:869: sngon tshe slob dpon pad+ma yis //
NK041(di)027:870: rgyags barngana chen mo 'di mdzad pas //
NK041(di)027:871: gtsug lag grub cing mtha' dmag thul //
NK041(di)027:872: rje yi dgongs pa 'grub pa dang //
NK041(di)027:873: bod khams bde skyid byung ba ltar //
NK041(di)027:874: bdag gis mgron rnams barngana pa yis //
NK041(di)027:875: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK041(di)027:876: 'khor rnams srung la rkyen rnams zlog /
NK041(di)027:877: tshe srings dpal skyed 'byor pa spel //
NK041(di)027:878: snyan pa sgrubs la grags pa sgrogs //
NK041(di)027:879: rtag tu 'go zhing sdong grogs mdzod //
NK041(di)027:880: mgron rnams bde zhing 'jigs pa med //
NK041(di)027:881: lam 'phrang bde bar bgrod pa dang //
NK041(di)027:882: rnyed pa chen po sgrub pa dang //
NK041(di)027:883: gzhi byes kun tu bde legs mdzod //
NK041(di)027:884: ces mgron rigs rnams barngana la /
NK041(di)027:885: gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga'i bzod gsol ni /
NK041(di)027:886: ma 'byor pa dang nyams pa dang //
NK041(di)027:887: gang yang bdag rmongs blo yis ni //
NK041(di)027:888: bgyis pa dang ni bgyid stsal pa //
NK041(di)027:889: de kun bzod par mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)027:890: badz+ra sat+wa sogs yi ge brgya pa dang /
NK041(di)027:891: +aa li k+aa lis lhag chad kha bskang /
NK041(di)027:892: de nas mgron rigs rnams gshegs su gsol ba ni //
NK041(di)027:893: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK041(di)027:894: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK041(di)027:895: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang //
NK041(di)027:896: sems can rnams kyi don slad du //
NK041(di)027:897: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)027:898: badz+ra muhzhesa pas ye shes pa rnams rang sar gshegs shing /
NK041(di)027:899: mchod sbyin gnas 'dir gang lhags pa'i //
NK041(di)027:902: sa blar rgyu ba gang yin pa //
NK041(di)027:903: mgu bar gyis la rang gnas su //
NK041(di)027:904: thams cad tha dad 'gro bar gyis //
NK041(di)027:905: sarba b+hu ta gats+tshah zhes pas 'byung po rnams rang
NK041(di)027:906: gnas su btang la bsngo ba dang smon lam gyis
NK041(di)027:908: bsangs ras dang sha chang la sogs pa'i dga' ston la rol /
NK041(di)027:909: rdo rje'i glu dang shin tu skyid pa'i bro brdung /
NK041(di)027:910: rjes su tshigs su bcad pa'i rjes la me tog
NK041(di)027:911: gi char dbab cing bkra shis pa'i tshigs su bcad
NK041(di)027:912: pa sogs brjod cing dga' ston gyi nyams bskyang /
NK041(di)027:913: 'di ltar rab dkar dge tshogs rnam dag mthus //
NK041(di)027:914: rdo rje snying po'i bstan pa dar ba dang //
NK041(di)027:915: de skyong bstan 'dzin skyes bu dam pa rnams //
NK041(di)027:916: zhabs pad bskal brgya'i bar du brtan gyur cig /
NK041(di)027:917: skye dgu sems can bde skyid kun ldan zhing //
NK041(di)027:918: lo phyugs rab rgyas tshe dpal ye shes rgyas //
NK041(di)027:919: 'gal rkyen kun zhi bsam don lhun gyis grub //
NK041(di)027:920: mthar thug chos la spyod pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK041(di)027:921: dkyil 'khor gzhal yas 'dir yang bkra shis shing //
NK041(di)027:922: nyin yang bkra shis dpal 'bar ta la la //
NK041(di)027:923: mtshan yang bkra shis dpal 'bar 'khyil li li //
NK041(di)027:924: nyin mtshan rtag tu bkra shis bde legs shog /
NK041(di)027:925: de ltar slob dpon sangs rgyas gnyis pa pad+m+aa ka
NK041(di)027:926: ras bsam yas sa 'dul gyi don du mdzad pa'i
NK041(di)027:927: rgyags barngana chen mo phan yon bsam las 'das pa
NK041(di)027:928: 'di nyid zur mkhar rdo'i mchod rten du sba bar
NK041(di)027:929: mdzad pa / rgyal sras legs pas spyan drangs pa
NK041(di)027:930: nyid bar skabs su dpe ma dag pa rgyun 'byams
NK041(di)027:931: mdzad pa / pa las / kun mkhyen chen po
NK041(di)027:932: klong chen rab 'byams bzang pos zhus dag par mdzad
NK041(di)027:933: mdzad pa / pa las / cing / de mthun
NK041(di)027:934: lha bsangs kyi cho ga bde legs kun 'byung zhes
NK041(di)027:935: pa mdzad de dpe so sor snang ba dang /
NK041(di)027:938: bdag bskyed mchod bstod sogs las gzhung gzhan la zhal 'phangs kyis ltos dgos par 'dug pas /
NK041(di)027:939: kun mkhyen rang gi yig cha las bsdus shing rang
NK041(di)027:940: bzo'i dri mas dben pa cho ga'i go rim nag
NK041(di)027:941: po 'gro shes chu 'bab ma'i tshul phyogs gcig tu
NK041(di)027:942: bsgrigs pa 'di ni thams cad mkhyen pa rdzogs pa'i
NK041(di)027:943: sangs rgyas tshul khrims rdo rje rigs bdag tu thob
NK041(di)027:944: pa'i ban chung phrin las lhun grub kyis ston gsum
NK041(di)027:945: rtsi bcud dang 'bras bu smiin pa'i dus su sgrub
NK041(di)027:946: rgyud kyi gdan sa dar rgyas chos gling du bkod
NK041(di)027:947: pa'i yi ge pa ni karma mchog 'gyur gyis bgyis
